OL,3,CFather on the run with three children
OL,4,Cspotted on CCTV in New Zealand
OL,6,FThomas Callam Phillips has been hiding
OL,7,Fhis children, Jayda, Maverick and
OL,8,FEmber, in the dense bush after taking
OL,9,Fthem from their home in Marokopa on
OL,10,Fthe Northern Island of New Zealand in
OL,11,FDecember 2021.
OL,13,FThe possible sighting comes after
OL,14,FPhillips' relatives last week appealed
OL,15,Ffor him to return home.
OL,17,FOn Friday, police released footage
OL,18,Fshowing two masked people loading
OL,19,Fitems into containers on a quad bike
OL,20,Foutside a shop in the western town of
OL,21,FPiopio.
