OL,3,CFather on the run with three children
OL,4,Cspotted on CCTV in New Zealand
OL,6,FThe incident occurred around 2am on
OL,7,FWednesday.
OL,9,FThe shop owner told local news outlet
OL,10,FRNZ that only milk was taken, despite
OL,11,Fvegetables and butter also being on
OL,12,Fdisplay.
OL,14,FHe said two people used an angle
OL,15,Fgrinder to cut the padlock on his
OL,16,Fshop's outdoor freezer, triggering the
OL,17,Falarm, and the pair grabbed some milk
OL,18,Fbefore fleeing on a quad bike.
