OL,3,CFather on the run with three children
OL,4,Cspotted on CCTV in New Zealand
OL,6,FOfficers are examining the CCTV for
OL,7,Fany link to Phillips, with the shop
OL,8,Fbeing one he is believed to have
OL,9,Funsuccessfully targeted in November
OL,10,F2023, Detective Senior Sergeant Andy
OL,11,FSaunders said.
OL,13,FPolice believe Phillips and his
OL,14,Fchildren are living off-grid, with the
OL,15,Ffather using his survival skills to
OL,16,Fprovide food, shelter and clothing.
OL,17,FThey also suspect supporters are
OL,18,Fhelping him to remain at large.
