OL,3,CFather on the run with three children
OL,4,Cspotted on CCTV in New Zealand
OL,6,FPhillips is accused of a series of
OL,7,Fcrimes, including an armed bank
OL,8,Frobbery in May 2023, when two people
OL,9,Fwere caught on CCTV fleeing on a
OL,10,Fmotorbike with cash.
OL,12,FHe already faces charges including
OL,13,Faggravated robbery, aggravated
OL,14,Fwounding, and unlawful possession of a
OL,15,Ffirearm.
OL,17,FIn November 2023, Phillips and an
OL,18,Funnamed child are alleged to have
OL,19,Fsmashed a shop window at 2am before
OL,20,Ffleeing on a stolen quad bike.
