OL,3,CFather on the run with three children
OL,4,Cspotted on CCTV in New Zealand
OL,6,FHe has also been spotted on CCTV, with
OL,7,Fhis face covered, buying supplies in a
OL,8,Fhardware shop.
OL,10,FIn her first interview since Phillips
OL,11,Fdisappeared, his sister Rozzi Phillips
OL,12,Ftold news outlets how much the family
OL,13,Fmisses him and wants him to come home.
OL,15,F"I miss you, and I miss being part of
OL,16,Fyour life," she said, her voice
OL,17,Fbreaking. "You're very special to
OL,18,Fme... I really want to see you again."
